args: Your Highness, we've received an urgent\nrequest for aid from the village of Nifal.
We've performed there a few times.\nWhat's going on? What happened?
It appears they have been assaulted by\nfiends and are in desperate need of aid.
You have to take me with you!
...That is the last of the fiends. But alas,\nthey already did a great deal of harm.
It used to be such a beautiful village,\nbut you'd never know that now.
I don't see any villagers here. I hope that\nmeans they were evacuated in time?
I'm guessin' they hightailed it outta here\nwhen they heard the fiends comin'.\n...Oh hey, wait! Look over there!
Did you and the troupe come all this way\nto perform for us?
Oh dear. I'm sorry that you've come\nat this terrible time.
We've no time for your fool circus, girl!
We have to rebuild our homes and lives,\nnot watch some merry gang of tumblers!
Hang on, people! You don't understand!
She came here to fight for you!\nTo try and HELP your villa—
It's okay. You don't need to defend me.
Look around you. Look what happened.\nYou can't blame them for thinking that\nI don't understand the situation.
But I can't turn my back on them, either...
So instead, we're going to help everyone\nhere get back on their feet!
Now THAT sounds like a plan!
*sigh* How are we supposed to get this\nheavy rubble out of the way?
I'm pretty sure we can do it together.
Ha! As if a mere entertainer could\npossibly lift this massive—
Egads! Where did HE come from?!
Good boy! Now carry all this rubble to\nthe outskirts of the village, okay?
Damn. Looks like I underestimated you.
Heh. That big circus tent doesn't set\nitself up, you know?
...Time to get rid of this pile of garbage.\nGo to it, Liger!
Wow! He picked it all up!
Right then! While he's dealing with that,\nlet's move on to the next pile.
...Gather round, everyone! We've got loads\nof our troupe's finest stew to go around!
If you want some, join the line!
She diced the vegetables so they look like\nlittle dragons! That's...so...cuuuuu...
This is some excellent work, young lady.
Aw, thanks! Oh, and there's plenty more,\nso please help yourself.
I'm actually not certain I can eat\nsomething this adorable.
Well, ya sure as hell can't leave it!\nThat would be a crime against humanity!
Fine, then! I'll eat it if you won't!\n*chomp* *horf* URRRRRK!
Did it get stuck in your throat, Ranzal?!
Honestly, what did you THINK would\nhappen when you shoved such a\nmassive spoonful into your mouth?
I'm fine! Sheesh! I just lost the ability\nto speak for a second there because\nit was so damn good.
*sigh* Is there no end to your idiocy?
Ha ha! Oh, but you are a funny lot!
La la laaaaa ♪ Right then! Who's next?\n...Oh! {player_name}!
Can these kids get some stew, Annelie?
Of course! Here's some for you...\nand some for you!
Have as much as you want, okay?\nI can always whip up more.
Looks like you know a lot of ways to\nmake people happy, don't you?
You've done more than just help rebuild—\nyou've lifted their spirits in the process.
It's hard to believe what a downtrodden\nbunch this was earlier.
Sure, but we all helped with that.
I'm just glad they're all smiling again.
Smiles are contagious, you know?\nAnd they're some of the best medicine\nfor tough times.
Excuse me? I don't mean to be forward,\nbut while you're here, would you mind...\nperforming for us?
We've got a lot of work ahead, and that\nwould give us an extra shot of energy.
I'd be happy to! ...Er, but it's going to\nbe just Liger and me; we're the only\nmembers of the troupe here right now.
Don't forget about us. We know a thing\nor three about the circus life, remember?
Ha! In that case, let's start the show!
